{{version030}}

{{flavour|Causes vines to grow from the ground. The vines will reach out and grab interlopers, dragging them towards any nearby trees.}}

'''Awaken Vines''' is a monster-only spell which causes monstrous [[snaplasher vine]]s to burst forth from a nearby [[tree]] tile, quickly seeking opponents out. Vines can cause [[constriction]], and drag opponents into reach of an [[Awaken Forest|awakened forest]]. These vines are worth no [[experience]], and will die as soon as the caster is killed.

{{monsters with spell}}
